{"tid":1775790,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黎明行動成功爭取手足被捕","createTime":"2019-12-09T05:26:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T05:34:05.000Z","uid":185416,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8174aa6dd0e1b9dc371a1d30d69dcd4206490850","tid":1775790,"uid":185416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T05:26:23.000Z","msg":"0938 #新聞 #appledaily <br />\n<br />\n【抗暴26周】抗爭者將軍澳堵路 便衣防暴湧出帶走3人<br />\n<br />\n網民今日發起「大三罷.黎明行動」，其中將軍澳寶康路有約10名男女抗爭者，將大型垃圾桶及沙發等推出馬路堵塞，但隨即被監視的便衣警員發現，「吹雞」召來近30名防暴警拉人，最終兩男一女被帶走。<br />\n<br />\n一名理大校園記者，亦拍攝到警方行動。他表示早於6時58分，有6至7名黑衣人在志蓮小學外的唐俊街與唐賢街交界堵路，及用噴漆噴巴士。當時一名喬裝成抗爭者的警員混入他們當中，但在其後拘捕行動中，確認那人是警員。校園記者稱，不清楚該名警員混入抗爭者中的動機，亦不知道他向各人講了什麼，但確實曾以為他是其中一份子。<br />\n<br />\n報導全文：<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191209&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=60357608\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191209%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D60357608&d=2Jo0d4zpMW7MEYOmRW2LdSEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=f3ea14ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20191209%26s%3D10829391%26a%3D60357608&h=4edf91ad\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20191209&amp;s=10829391&amp;a=60357608</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好再搞黎明啦，一班唔敢罷工/唔想罷工嘅人，你永遠唔會阻到佢返工嫁，佢地打完十號，成條街爛撚晒都爬返工，怕你幾個rb?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後仲要搞到手足被捕<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n冇工會帶頭唔好再罷</span>"},{"pid":"2e8987b1569ab33342c02ad2288620c188e2b70c","tid":1775790,"uid":185416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T05:28:50.000Z","msg":"為呢班唔肯罷工嘅仆街被捕<br />\n值得咩"},{"pid":"94a0992fe453c16fcfa3e84e155ef4912d4c61ef","tid":1775790,"uid":36065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T05:28:51.000Z","msg":"咪再用ROAD BLOCK<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3ff1b66e8c3e5a93d4348f3634fabf1a5dffa7c","tid":1775790,"uid":258598,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T05:29:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5191f56c507d1dd43122afabd1d042d4f7d683d0","tid":1775790,"uid":185416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c3ff1b66e8c3e5a93d4348f3634fabf1a5dffa7c","tid":1775790,"uid":258598,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e8987b1569ab33342c02ad2288620c188e2b70c","tid":1775790,"uid":185416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T05:28:50.000Z","msg":"為呢班唔肯罷工嘅仆街被捕<br />\n值得咩"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T05:29:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T05:34:05.000Z","msg":"好無謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留返條命等機會啦"}]}